    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DunHero</strong> is Fantasy Action Roguelite</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a hero to start your journey in different worlds. Each hero has different starting items and strengths. The deeper you go, the more items you will find to help you and the stronger you will become</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is always something new waiting for you in <strong>Dunhero</strong> - such as a trader, a powerful item or a powerful enemy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270210/extras/ff41579939014dc8f9a04112ff7c0214.poster.avif?t=1771586233\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270210/extras/ff41579939014dc8f9a04112ff7c0214.webm?t=1771586233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270210/extras/ff41579939014dc8f9a04112ff7c0214.mp4?t=1771586233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DunHero in a nutshell</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >600+ Items </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >28 Playable Classes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80+ Rare Cards gained from leveling up </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Worlds with their bosses and enemies </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play With Your Friends!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather a team of 2-4 players and enjoy Multiplayer CO-OP experienc</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270210/extras/73fd9a3a91eefc0485b58f3522fea57e.poster.avif?t=1771586233\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270210/extras/73fd9a3a91eefc0485b58f3522fea57e.webm?t=1771586233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270210/extras/73fd9a3a91eefc0485b58f3522fea57e.mp4?t=1771586233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get Powerful Items and Cards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In DunHero there is a lot of items and cards from leveling up to create great build</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270210/extras/b229d0fb05af1c4ecf3b8629c1473c77.poster.avif?t=1771586233\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270210/extras/b229d0fb05af1c4ecf3b8629c1473c77.webm?t=1771586233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270210/extras/b229d0fb05af1c4ecf3b8629c1473c77.mp4?t=1771586233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pick Your Class!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play many Classes, each with different starting Items and strengths</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270210/extras/f3b365e0ab0fcc00fd707e16e52b5071.poster.avif?t=1771586233\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270210/extras/f3b365e0ab0fcc00fd707e16e52b5071.webm?t=1771586233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270210/extras/f3b365e0ab0fcc00fd707e16e52b5071.mp4?t=1771586233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Procedurally Generated Maps!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world and dungeons changes each time you play. So none of the gameplay will be the same! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come play <strong>Dunhero</strong> - every game is a new fun adventure!</p>",
